        "text": "Carved of driftwood stained white with the salt of the sea, a *pirate staff* has jewels and gold pieces embedded in the wood. A skull and crossbones sit on top. When used as a weapon, the staff is a *+2 striking fearsome staff*. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Intimidation checks to Coerce.",
